Error-[XMREM] Cross-module reference resolution error
testbench.sv, 67
"_if.tb.cb.c"
  Cross-module reference resolution error, illegal use of modport.
  

TimeScale is 1 ns / 1 ps
7 errors

Wrap your _if.tb.cb.c references inside @(_if.tb.cb) blocks.

Do not do assignments or reads on modport signals outside clocking block event context.

This will eliminate the "Cross-module reference resolution error".
